high_descs: Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and take the closest tomato on the top shelf of the lower compartment out of the fridge.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean tomato.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the table, then turn right to face the small black shelving unit in between the counter and trash bag.
Put the clean tomato on the top of the black shelving unit to the left of the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato on top of the black shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn to the left and then the right to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and take out a tomato, shut the door.
Carry the tomato a few steps to the left to locate the sink.
Place the tomato inside the sink, turn the water on then off, and pick up the tomato.
Take the tomato and move a few steps to the left to late the small black table.
Place the tomato on the left side of the black table.
anns.task_desc: Take a tomato from the fridge and rinse it. Then place it on the table.

high_descs: Move to the fridge to the left of the door
Get a tomato from the fridge and close the door
Move to the sink to the left of the fridge
Clean the tomato in the sink and pick it back up
Move to the end table to the left of the sink
Place the tomato on the end table
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned, chilled tomato on the black end table.
